===街頭示威===
在行刑後已有數次示威。在沙地阿拉伯[[東部省_(沙特阿拉伯)|東部省]]中的[[蓋提夫|蓋提夫]]地區，人們由尼姆爾家鄉{{le|al-Awamiyah|al-Awamiyah}}遊行至蓋提夫，高叫「打倒[[沙地王朝|沙地]]（王朝）」口號<ref name=presstv1 />。1月2日在處決同一天，示威者在伊朗首都[[德黑蘭|德黑蘭]]的沙地阿拉伯大使館聚集，其中一人對使館投擲自製燃燒彈後著火，示威在當地清晨3時後仍然繼續<ref>{{cite web|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2016/01/02/middleeast/saudi-arabia-executes-dozens-terror/|title=Tehran protest after Saudi Arabia executes Shiite cleric - CNN.com|author=Yousuf Basil, Salma Abdelaziz and Michael Pearson, CNN|date=2 January 2016|work=CNN|accessdate=3 January 2016|archive-date=2018-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181211102815/https://edition.cnn.com/2016/01/02/middleeast/saudi-arabia-executes-dozens-terror/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。伊朗警察以襲擊大使館為由拘捕當中40名示威者<ref>{{cite news|last1=Loveluck|first1=Louisa|title=Iran supreme leader says Saudi faces 'divine revenge'|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/saudiarabia/12077919/Saudi-Arabia-beheadings-highest-in-two-decades.html|accessdate=4 January 2016|work=Telegraph.co.uk|archive-date=2018-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180927065852/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/saudiarabia/12077919/Saudi-Arabia-beheadings-highest-in-two-decades.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Basil|first1=Yousuf|last2=Abdelaziz|first2=Salma|last3=Pearson|first3=Michael|title=Tehran protest after Saudi Arabia executes Shiite cleric - CNN.com|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2016/01/02/middleeast/saudi-arabia-executes-dozens-terror/|accessdate=4 January 2016|work=CNN|archive-date=2018-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181211102815/https://edition.cnn.com/2016/01/02/middleeast/saudi-arabia-executes-dozens-terror/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Staff writers|title=Farsnews|url=http://en.farsnews.com/newstext.aspx?nn=13941013000588|accessdate=4 January 2016|work=en.farsnews.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160109230609/http://en.farsnews.com/newstext.aspx?nn=13941013000588|archive-date=2016-01-09|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

數百人在[[巴林|巴林]]首都[[麥納瑪|麥納瑪]]舉行示威<ref name=presstv2 />。帶著謝赫尼姆爾的畫像的示威者於巴林村落{{le|Abu-Saiba|Abu-Saiba}}與警察發生衝突<ref name=independent />。另外數百人於巴林{{le|al-Daih|al-Daih}}和{{le|Sitra|Sitra}}遊行，高叫反對沙地阿拉伯統治沙特王朝家族和巴林統治遜尼派家族的標語，並叫尼姆爾「我們的烈士」<ref>{{cite news|script-title=en:The Latest: Insider says Saudis decided ‘enough was enough’|url=http://www.wtvq.com/2016/01/03/the-latest-insider-says-saudis-decided-enough-was-enough/|publisher=[[WTVQ-DT|WTVQ-DT]] (AP)|date=3 January 2016|accessdate=4 January 2016|title=存档副本|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160104041833/http://www.wtvq.com/2016/01/03/the-latest-insider-says-saudis-decided-enough-was-enough/|archive-date=2016-01-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

數百名群眾闖入仍未工式開啟的沙地阿拉伯駐[[伊拉克|伊拉克]]大使館<ref>{{cite web|url=http://en.trend.az/world/arab/2476659.html|title=Protesters break into Saudi embassy in Baghdad|date=4 January 2016|work=Trend|access-date=2016-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310084906/http://en.trend.az/world/arab/2476659.html|archive-date=2016-03-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，媒體亦公開了一段沙地阿拉伯[[巴格達|巴格達]]伊館被火箭炮攻擊的片段<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.presstv.ir/Detail/2016/01/04/444389/Baghdad-Saudi-embassy-rocket-attack/|title=PressTV|publisher=|accessdate=2016-02-12|archive-date=2017-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170313032404/http://www.presstv.ir/Detail/2016/01/04/444389/Baghdad-Saudi-embassy-rocket-attack/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

群眾在[[印度|印度]][[查謨-克什米爾邦|查謨-克什米爾邦]]首府[[斯利那加|斯利那加]]高舉反沙地橫額示威。示威者遊行往聯合國辦公室，被警察截停。類似的示威於[[卡基爾縣|卡基爾縣]]亦有舉行，宗教團體呼籲舉行為期3日的哀悼<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.greaterkashmir.com/news/kashmir/ayatollah-nimr-s-execution-aftermath/206021.html|title=Ayatollah Nimr's Execution Aftermath|publisher=[[Greater_Kashmir|Greater Kashmir]]|date=4 January 2015|accessdate=2016-01-04|archive-date=2019-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190102050432/https://www.greaterkashmir.com/news/kashmir/ayatollah-nimr-s-execution-aftermath/206021.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2016年1月5日，印度[[拉達克|拉達克]]有來自[[列城|列城]]和[[卡爾吉爾|卡爾吉爾]]的[[佛教|佛教]]、[[基督教|基督教]]和[[伊斯蘭教|伊斯蘭教]]（遜尼及什葉派）團體舉行了[[燭光集會|燭光集會]]，表示對人權活動的支持及反對處決尼姆爾<ref>{{cite web |author= Raqib Hameed Naik |url= http://twocircles.net/2016jan05/1452013224.html#.VpVdXrZ96zc |title= Leh residents unite to protest against Shia cleric's execution, organise candle light march |work= TwoCircles.net |date= January 5, 2016 |accessdate= January 12, 2016 |archive-date= 2018-09-29 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20180929102709/http://twocircles.net/2016jan05/1452013224.html#.VpVdXrZ96zc |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

其它一些地方也发生了和平示威，如伊朗聖地[[庫姆|庫姆]]和[[馬什哈德|馬什哈德]]、[[黎巴嫩|黎巴嫩]]、[[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]]和[[土耳其|土耳其]]。

