tps://web.archive.org/web/20160105031615/http://www.presstv.ir/Detail/2016/01/02/444201/Iran-Makarem-Shirazi-NouriHamedani-SafiGolpaygani-Nimr/|archive-date=2016-01-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。[[伊朗專家會議|伊朗專家會議]]中代表伊朗西南部[[錫斯坦－俾路支斯坦省|錫斯坦－俾路支斯坦省]]的遜尼派人士、[[伊斯蘭議會|伊斯蘭議會]]遜尼派議員團主席Abed Fattahi以及[[扎黑丹|扎黑丹]]星期五祈禱帶領者Molawi Abdolhamid Ismailzehi等众多遜尼派教士均譴責處決。伊朗各神學院在沙地德黑蘭大使館前舉行示威，譴責對尼姆爾的處決并高叫「[[沙地王朝|沙地]]（王朝）去死」的口號<ref name=fars1>{{cite web|url=http://en.farsnews.com/newstext.aspx?nn=13941012001441|publisher=Farsnews|title=IRGC: Sheikh Nimr's Execution Displays ISIL-Like Behavior Saudi Regime's Behavior|date=2 January 2016|access-date=2016-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160107084828/http://en.farsnews.com/newstext.aspx?nn=13941012001441|archive-date=2016-01-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。一群伊朗宗教領袖及神學院學生亦在什葉派聖地[[馬什哈德|馬什哈德]]和[[庫姆|庫姆]]示威<ref name="presstv.ir1">{{cite web|url=http://www.presstv.ir/Detail/2016/01/03/444321/Iran-Tehran-Saudi-Arabia-Nimr-/|title=PressTV|publisher=|accessdate=3 January 2016|archive-date=2016-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160107212026/http://www.presstv.ir/Detail/2016/01/03/444321/Iran-Tehran-Saudi-Arabia-Nimr-/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
